iBoard 2.0 is a basic framework for any RAILS CMS and Blogging-System. 
It handles the basics which are needed by any web-application (Users, Postings/Articles, 
Binary-files, newsletters and so on)

see http://iboard.cc/pages/10/show_page for more information
Find iBoard at http://github.com/iboard/iboard if you want to fetch the source.

June 2008, Andi Altendorfer, Haid, Austria

  Have Fun!

